<codeline><highlight class="normal">###<sp/>Reading<sp/>and<sp/>Setting<sp/>Atmega<sp/>Fuses<sp/>with<sp/>avrdude</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">We&apos;re<sp/>going<sp/>to<sp/>need<sp/>to<sp/>set<sp/>some<sp/>fuses<sp/>for<sp/>our<sp/>part<sp/>in<sp/>the<sp/>factory.<sp/><sp/>The<sp/>fuse<sp/>settings<sp/>we<sp/>need<sp/>are<sp/>going<sp/>to<sp/>set<sp/>our<sp/>part<sp/>to<sp/>basically<sp/>should</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">match<sp/>the<sp/>Arduino<sp/>Pro<sp/>defaults<sp/>with<sp/>brownout<sp/>disabled.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">At<sp/>the<sp/>time<sp/>of<sp/>writing,<sp/>I<sp/>don&apos;t<sp/>have<sp/>a<sp/>programmer<sp/>at<sp/>my<sp/>disposal.<sp/><sp/>However<sp/>the<sp/>steps<sp/>taken<sp/>should<sp/>be<sp/>the<sp/></highlight></codeline>
