<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Steps:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">1.<sp/>Install<sp/>avrdude.<sp/><sp/>I<sp/>used<sp/>[http://www.obdev.at/products/crosspack/index.html](CrossPack)<sp/>to<sp/>do<sp/>this.</highlight></codeline>
