<codeline><highlight class="normal">1.<sp/>Go<sp/>to<sp/>[http://www.engbedded.com/fusecalc/](The<sp/>Avr<sp/>Fuse<sp/>Calculator)<sp/>and<sp/>enter<sp/>in<sp/>the<sp/>current<sp/>state<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>fuses</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">1.<sp/>Turn<sp/>off<sp/>Brown<sp/>Out<sp/>Detection<sp/>(BOD).</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">1.<sp/>Calculate<sp/>the<sp/>new<sp/>state<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>fuses<sp/>using<sp/>the<sp/>website,<sp/>note<sp/>for<sp/>future<sp/>(so<sp/>no<sp/>one<sp/>else<sp/>has<sp/>to<sp/>do<sp/>these<sp/>silly<sp/>instructions)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">1.<sp/>Use<sp/>avrdude<sp/>to<sp/>write<sp/>and<sp/>test<sp/>your<sp/>new<sp/>fuse<sp/>settings.<sp/><sp/>The<sp/>command<sp/>line<sp/>will<sp/>look<sp/>something<sp/>like<sp/>this<sp/>(except,<sp/>these<sp/>are<sp/>guessed<sp/>values:<sp/>`avrdude<sp/>-p<sp/>atmega328p<sp/>-c<sp/>usbtiny<sp/>-U<sp/>lfuse:w:0xee:m<sp/>-U<sp/>hfuse:w:0xdc:m<sp/>-U<sp/>efuse:w:0xff:m`)</highlight></codeline>
